{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/designing-with-storybook/","webpackCompilationHash":"b54670cf2f883e6a2138","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":":heart: React","author":"Metamn"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4f296020-bc49-5a10-9af6-c8156804de78","excerpt":"No one can imagine how much creativity gone lost while we had no Storybook or an alternative.","html":"<p>No one can imagine how much creativity gone lost while we had no Storybook or an alternative.</p>\n<!--more-->\n<p>Storybook (<a href=\"http://metamn.io/mr-ui/\">live on metamn</a>) is a user interface development environment. Up until now we had integrated development environments (IDE) for any kind of development <em>but</em> UI.</p>\n<p>Now with Storybook you are able to:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Tweak</strong> live your work to find edge cases.</li>\n<li><strong>Test</strong> it instantly in different contexts like backgrounds and viewports.</li>\n<li>Have immediate <strong>accessibility</strong> feedback.</li>\n<li><strong>Document</strong> your work and experiments beautifully.</li>\n<li><strong>Save</strong> every experiment you do for curiosity and later reuse.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>And the list is continuously expanding. For me the best part is saving the experiments.</p>\n<p>I’m creating experimental user interfaces where every piece of UI on the screen is handmade. More, every single UI piece fits the underlying content which changes from site to site, brand to brand.</p>\n<p>This takes lots of experimentation. Just take a look at Lynx &#x26; Hare, a landing page I’ve created recently, and unfortunately not with React and Storybook.</p>\n<p>For this project I had no input (zero questions answered in the Design Brief) just ‘let it be something like between retro gaming and finance’.</p>\n<p>After I’ve sketched up the first version the direction suddenly went to minimal, <em>my style</em>, — I’ve even added a PacMan !!! which I had to throw out. Together with that retro button bringing back that 90s feeling.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/react/static/de42c519f59b2fd4589ae0c647c43cb1/12f40/lynx-pacman.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Bye Pacman!\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/react/static/de42c519f59b2fd4589ae0c647c43cb1/b9e4f/lynx-pacman.png\"\n        srcset=\"/react/static/de42c519f59b2fd4589ae0c647c43cb1/cf440/lynx-pacman.png 148w,\n/react/static/de42c519f59b2fd4589ae0c647c43cb1/d2d38/lynx-pacman.png 295w,\n/react/static/de42c519f59b2fd4589ae0c647c43cb1/b9e4f/lynx-pacman.png 590w,\n/react/static/de42c519f59b2fd4589ae0c647c43cb1/f9b6a/lynx-pacman.png 885w,\n/react/static/de42c519f59b2fd4589ae0c647c43cb1/2d849/lynx-pacman.png 1180w,\n/react/static/de42c519f59b2fd4589ae0c647c43cb1/12f40/lynx-pacman.png 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/react/static/d09f4f3a3fd6111e773cfbe4aa815050/12f40/lynx-button.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"That button!\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/react/static/d09f4f3a3fd6111e773cfbe4aa815050/b9e4f/lynx-button.png\"\n        srcset=\"/react/static/d09f4f3a3fd6111e773cfbe4aa815050/cf440/lynx-button.png 148w,\n/react/static/d09f4f3a3fd6111e773cfbe4aa815050/d2d38/lynx-button.png 295w,\n/react/static/d09f4f3a3fd6111e773cfbe4aa815050/b9e4f/lynx-button.png 590w,\n/react/static/d09f4f3a3fd6111e773cfbe4aa815050/f9b6a/lynx-button.png 885w,\n/react/static/d09f4f3a3fd6111e773cfbe4aa815050/2d849/lynx-button.png 1180w,\n/react/static/d09f4f3a3fd6111e773cfbe4aa815050/12f40/lynx-button.png 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>After creating <em>my style</em> …</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/react/static/a6c1fd292219ee5b2e9c9c6625b7dafa/12f40/lynx-my-style.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"My style\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/react/static/a6c1fd292219ee5b2e9c9c6625b7dafa/b9e4f/lynx-my-style.png\"\n        srcset=\"/react/static/a6c1fd292219ee5b2e9c9c6625b7dafa/cf440/lynx-my-style.png 148w,\n/react/static/a6c1fd292219ee5b2e9c9c6625b7dafa/d2d38/lynx-my-style.png 295w,\n/react/static/a6c1fd292219ee5b2e9c9c6625b7dafa/b9e4f/lynx-my-style.png 590w,\n/react/static/a6c1fd292219ee5b2e9c9c6625b7dafa/f9b6a/lynx-my-style.png 885w,\n/react/static/a6c1fd292219ee5b2e9c9c6625b7dafa/2d849/lynx-my-style.png 1180w,\n/react/static/a6c1fd292219ee5b2e9c9c6625b7dafa/12f40/lynx-my-style.png 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>… still the result was not good enough, so I’ve created a third variant.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/react/static/3c71727b3b487527857995077ebe0218/12f40/lynx-5b.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"I don't know whose style!\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/react/static/3c71727b3b487527857995077ebe0218/b9e4f/lynx-5b.png\"\n        srcset=\"/react/static/3c71727b3b487527857995077ebe0218/cf440/lynx-5b.png 148w,\n/react/static/3c71727b3b487527857995077ebe0218/d2d38/lynx-5b.png 295w,\n/react/static/3c71727b3b487527857995077ebe0218/b9e4f/lynx-5b.png 590w,\n/react/static/3c71727b3b487527857995077ebe0218/f9b6a/lynx-5b.png 885w,\n/react/static/3c71727b3b487527857995077ebe0218/2d849/lynx-5b.png 1180w,\n/react/static/3c71727b3b487527857995077ebe0218/12f40/lynx-5b.png 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>I wish I had Storybook at design time. Now all my work would be nicely cataloged, documented, buttons would stick together with other buttons, fonts in the same way, color schemes with another colors schemes,\nand in plus I would have live all those variations I have now only as screenshots somewhere on my hard drive.</p>\n<p>A variant on red:</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/react/static/e6fe643a0541835f38b764bb89b7f4e1/8b984/lynx-5b-red.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 62.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"The last variant in red\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/react/static/e6fe643a0541835f38b764bb89b7f4e1/b9e4f/lynx-5b-red.png\"\n        srcset=\"/react/static/e6fe643a0541835f38b764bb89b7f4e1/cf440/lynx-5b-red.png 148w,\n/react/static/e6fe643a0541835f38b764bb89b7f4e1/d2d38/lynx-5b-red.png 295w,\n/react/static/e6fe643a0541835f38b764bb89b7f4e1/b9e4f/lynx-5b-red.png 590w,\n/react/static/e6fe643a0541835f38b764bb89b7f4e1/f9b6a/lynx-5b-red.png 885w,\n/react/static/e6fe643a0541835f38b764bb89b7f4e1/2d849/lynx-5b-red.png 1180w,\n/react/static/e6fe643a0541835f38b764bb89b7f4e1/8b984/lynx-5b-red.png 2560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>This one with a Canvas background and particles moving with the cursor.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/react/static/55bf7d6e5c2bdfe9ef13926215c0535c/8b984/lynx-5b-gradient.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 62.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"The last variant with canvas gradient\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/react/static/55bf7d6e5c2bdfe9ef13926215c0535c/b9e4f/lynx-5b-gradient.png\"\n        srcset=\"/react/static/55bf7d6e5c2bdfe9ef13926215c0535c/cf440/lynx-5b-gradient.png 148w,\n/react/static/55bf7d6e5c2bdfe9ef13926215c0535c/d2d38/lynx-5b-gradient.png 295w,\n/react/static/55bf7d6e5c2bdfe9ef13926215c0535c/b9e4f/lynx-5b-gradient.png 590w,\n/react/static/55bf7d6e5c2bdfe9ef13926215c0535c/f9b6a/lynx-5b-gradient.png 885w,\n/react/static/55bf7d6e5c2bdfe9ef13926215c0535c/2d849/lynx-5b-gradient.png 1180w,\n/react/static/55bf7d6e5c2bdfe9ef13926215c0535c/8b984/lynx-5b-gradient.png 2560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Or these, a completely new iteration with type set on a dynamic cell matrix.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/react/static/efbe4649b9b4566ae43ea27e5ecc60f3/12f40/lynx-4a.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Type on a matrix\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/react/static/efbe4649b9b4566ae43ea27e5ecc60f3/b9e4f/lynx-4a.png\"\n        srcset=\"/react/static/efbe4649b9b4566ae43ea27e5ecc60f3/cf440/lynx-4a.png 148w,\n/react/static/efbe4649b9b4566ae43ea27e5ecc60f3/d2d38/lynx-4a.png 295w,\n/react/static/efbe4649b9b4566ae43ea27e5ecc60f3/b9e4f/lynx-4a.png 590w,\n/react/static/efbe4649b9b4566ae43ea27e5ecc60f3/f9b6a/lynx-4a.png 885w,\n/react/static/efbe4649b9b4566ae43ea27e5ecc60f3/2d849/lynx-4a.png 1180w,\n/react/static/efbe4649b9b4566ae43ea27e5ecc60f3/12f40/lynx-4a.png 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>On gray background:</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/react/static/734cbb74ecb15b19b9946f59078291db/12f40/lynx-4a-gray.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Type on a matrix, gray\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/react/static/734cbb74ecb15b19b9946f59078291db/b9e4f/lynx-4a-gray.png\"\n        srcset=\"/react/static/734cbb74ecb15b19b9946f59078291db/cf440/lynx-4a-gray.png 148w,\n/react/static/734cbb74ecb15b19b9946f59078291db/d2d38/lynx-4a-gray.png 295w,\n/react/static/734cbb74ecb15b19b9946f59078291db/b9e4f/lynx-4a-gray.png 590w,\n/react/static/734cbb74ecb15b19b9946f59078291db/f9b6a/lynx-4a-gray.png 885w,\n/react/static/734cbb74ecb15b19b9946f59078291db/2d849/lynx-4a-gray.png 1180w,\n/react/static/734cbb74ecb15b19b9946f59078291db/12f40/lynx-4a-gray.png 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>… and the underlying cell matrix. I don’t have the rotated and skewed screenshots — they are neat!</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/react/static/32c87651a0ff9c9d0e9ec4ec4d46a4e3/8b984/lynx-matrix.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 62.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"The cell matrix\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/react/static/32c87651a0ff9c9d0e9ec4ec4d46a4e3/b9e4f/lynx-matrix.png\"\n        srcset=\"/react/static/32c87651a0ff9c9d0e9ec4ec4d46a4e3/cf440/lynx-matrix.png 148w,\n/react/static/32c87651a0ff9c9d0e9ec4ec4d46a4e3/d2d38/lynx-matrix.png 295w,\n/react/static/32c87651a0ff9c9d0e9ec4ec4d46a4e3/b9e4f/lynx-matrix.png 590w,\n/react/static/32c87651a0ff9c9d0e9ec4ec4d46a4e3/f9b6a/lynx-matrix.png 885w,\n/react/static/32c87651a0ff9c9d0e9ec4ec4d46a4e3/2d849/lynx-matrix.png 1180w,\n/react/static/32c87651a0ff9c9d0e9ec4ec4d46a4e3/8b984/lynx-matrix.png 2560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Now I’ve <a href=\"http://metamn.io/mr-ui/?selectedKind=Playground&#x26;selectedStory=Lynx%20%26%20Hare&#x26;full=0&#x26;addons=1&#x26;stories=1&#x26;panelRight=0&#x26;addonPanel=storybook-addon-background%2Fbackground-panel&#x26;background=beige\">saved the project to Storybook</a>, at least the layout. You can play with live. And I’ll use it as a demo project across the entire UI library in the future.</p>\n<p>Just to remind me to be thankful for Storybook every time I use.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Designing with Storybook","date":"December 14, 2018"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/designing-with-storybook/","previous":{"excerpt":"WordPress is here with Gutenberg — it’s time to react.","fields":{"slug":"/to-react-with-best-practices/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"To React with best practices"}},"next":{"excerpt":"With React — a reactive / responsive framework — it’s time to rethink the responsiveness of a website.","fields":{"slug":"/four-types-of-responsiveness-in-react/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Four types of responsiveness in React"}}}}}